  - q: "Ceramic coating vs wax: Which is better?"
    a: >-
      While ceramic coatings give a thicker, longer-lasting protective layer,
      wax gives a brief gloss. Ceramic coating is the better option for
      long-term protection.
  - q: "Will ceramic coating prevent scratches?"
    a: >-
      Ceramic coatings provide a strong protective layer that helps resist
      minor scratches and swirl marks, but they are not completely
      scratch-proof.
  - q: "Does ceramic coating require special maintenance?"
